      "rationale": "Linear elastic titanium alloy (Ti-6Al-4V) constitutive model appropriate for sub-yield predictions; elasto-plastic model employed for post-yield regime with bilinear isotropic hardening calibrated to tensile coupon data. Augmented Lagrange contact formulation selected for screw-rod interface. Model form assumptions documented in simulation plan."
