      "rationale": "Material properties (E, yield stress, tangent modulus) sourced from lot-specific tensile coupon testing (n=5 per lot). Geometric dimensions obtained from CMM measurements of test specimens. Input uncertainty distributions assigned based on measurement data and propagated through the model via Monte Carlo sampling (10,000 runs), yielding probabilistic QoI distributions reported alongside deterministic predictions."
