      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single load configuration per ASTM F1717 standard protocol. While the standard configuration is clinically representative, only one test condition was evaluated, limiting the ability to characterize model response across the broader loading space. This factor falls below the required level; the gap is noted and accepted given the strong experimental correlation observed at the tested condition."
    },
